text:
coc-pythonの設定いじりたくてCocConfig書いてるんですが、オプションどこに置けばいいんだろう....
<https://github.com/neoclide/coc-python#options>
↑このへんで、CocConfigは現状これです
```{
  "languageserver": {
    "python": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": [
        "-mpyls",
        "-vv",
        "--log-file",
        "/tmp/lsp_python.log"
      ],
      "trace.server": "verbose",
      "filetypes": [
        "python"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "pyls": {
          "enable": true,
        "   trace": {
          "  server": "verbose"
          },
        "  commandPath": "",
        "  configurationSources": [
          "  pycodestyle"
          ],
        "  plugins": {
          }
	}
      }
    }
  }
}```
